# Enforce LF line endings for all text files in this repo.
#
# The install.ps1 integrity check compares the downloaded GameOptimizerPro.ps1
# against a fixed SHA256 hash (see CHECKSUMS.txt). That hash is line-ending
# sensitive: if the file were ever committed with CRLF, raw.githubusercontent
# would serve different bytes and the checksum would fail for every user.
# Pinning LF here keeps the published hash stable no matter which OS commits.

* text=auto eol=lf
*.ps1 text eol=lf
*.md  text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
